      <title><![CDATA[Introduction]]></title>
        <descriptionText><![CDATA[<Introtext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; color:#cc0033; margin:10px; padding:0 0 0 5px; background:#e8e8e8; border-bottom:1px solid #333; display:block;">Welcome</Introtext><welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">Welcome to the <b> OAPI Sales Accelerator Simulation. </b><br>In this fourth round of the simulation you’ll use the skills you have acquired to practice what you have learned in the session and to close appropriately at each phase of the prescribing cycle.<BR><BR>This round of the simulation will include six decisions, and should take you 20 to 30 minutes. Each of the possible questions you consider has been rated according to the following individual metrics, so your score will reflect whether your decision making is in line with these characteristics:<BR><BR><b>Scoring Metrics:</b><BR><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; padding-left:20px;">Customer’s Needs </span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions will help you better understand your customers’ treatment goals for their patients</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions will capture new opportunities for the customer</li><br><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; padding-left:20px;">Sales Progress</span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions build on previous discussions and align with where the customer is in their<span style="margin:0 0 0 15px;"> prescribing cycle</span></li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions advance the sale by "closing" at multiple points in the prescribing cycle</li><BR><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; padding-left:20px;">Trusted Advisor Relationship </span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions demonstrate a deep understanding of the customer's priorities and goals</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions genuinely engage the customer by partnering with the customer to create value</li></welcomeText><lasttext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; color:#000; background-color:#c0c0c0; margin:10px; padding:2px 0 2px 5px; display:block;">Please tap <b>Continue</b>  or swipe to see information about you and your customer.</lasttext><welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><BR><BR><I><B>Simulation Version: January 2012   0711T-3576D</B></I></welcomeText>]]></descriptionText>
